{"word":"ἄποινα","slug":"ἄποινα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n12700\" key=\"a)/poina\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἄποινα</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>, (by haplology for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπό-ποινα </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ποινή,</etym>) cf. <sense id=\"n12700.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀπετίνυτο ποινήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:398\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.398</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰ χρήματα ἄποινα ὠνόμαζον οἱ παλαιοί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg023.perseus-grc1:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.33</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>): </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n12700.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> (only in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> </bibl>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ransom</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">price paid,</tr_> whether <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to recover one's freedom</tr_> when taken prisoner, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φέρων ἀπερείσι᾽ ἄ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScop